(4144, 142, 'tours_include', '<!--:en--><ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Half day City Tour Cusco y Ruinas Sacsayhuaman, Qenqo, Tambomachay y Puca – Pucará. </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Full day Excursion to Machu Picchu: Expedition train or   Executive class from Ollanta. </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Touristic bus ticket Cusco – Puno: entries + buffet lunch. </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Full day Titicaca Lake: Uros Island and Taquile + lunch </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salt Cathedral</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">City tour in Bogotà with monserrate</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Coffee experience in San Alberto</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tour to Filandia, Cocora and Salento</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">City tour through Cartagena, regular service.</span></li>\r\n</ul><!--:--><!--:zh-->盐大教堂 在波哥大与蒙塞拉特市游览 在卡利城市观光 显示晚餐 参观西尔维娅和波帕扬 在阿尔贝托的咖啡体验 Filandia，Cocora和Salento参观 麦德林城市观光定期服务 您可以选择以下活动：Tour ofGuatapé，Santa fe de Antioquia或ParqueArví以及silletera文化。 圣玛尔塔市旅游，定期服务 游览泰罗纳公园，可以选择：Cañaveral或Neguanje。 通过卡塔赫纳市游览，定期服务。<!--:-->'),
