(290, 1, '2018-08-07 18:35:58', '2018-08-07 18:35:58', '[:zh]这座哥伦比亚的美丽城市被宣告为世界文化遗产，同时蕴藏了所有人都为之倾心的历史性殖民期宝藏。 漫步其绚丽多姿的城市街道，您可以在平均30摄氏度的常温气候下，品味并沉浸于其富有特色的标志性建筑群之中。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-291\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cartagena-1-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"cartagena\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n此外，一份独特且奢华的旅游&amp;酒店优惠将为您的假期锦上添花。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-292\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cartagena-2-336x220.jpg\" alt=\"cartagena\" width=\"336\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n城墙、阳台、彩车与石头街道构成了这个城市最具特色的标志性景观，同时也成为殖民地时期的特征。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-293\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cartagena-3-427x220.jpg\" alt=\"cartagena\" width=\"427\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n为您的下一次旅游记录下这一目的地，保证您会爱不释手。 了解更多请点击 -&gt;\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:en]This beautiful city of Colombia declared a World Heritage Site, hides a history and colonial treasures that enamors all who visit it. While walking through its colorful streets, you can enjoy its characteristic architecture, while enjoying its warm climate of 30 ° C average.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-291\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cartagena-1-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"cartagena\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nIn addition, its great tourist and hotel offer, make your vacation a unique and luxurious experience.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-292\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cartagena-2-336x220.jpg\" alt=\"cartagena\" width=\"336\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nIts walls, balconies, floats and stone streets are the most characteristic attractions of this city, becoming a colonial spectacle.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-293\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cartagena-3-427x220.jpg\" alt=\"cartagena\" width=\"427\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nWrite down this destination on your next vacation, you will love it! Learn more details here -&gt;<!--more-->[:]', '[:zh]卡塔赫纳，一个坐拥一切的旅游目的地[:en]Cartagena, a destination that has everything.[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'cartagena-a-destination-that-has-everything', '', '', '2018-08-16 20:51:02', '2018-08-16 20:51:02', '', 0, 'https://anditrip.com/?p=290', 0, 'post', '', 0),
