(295, 1, '2018-08-07 19:40:07', '2018-08-07 19:40:07', '[:zh]秘鲁是一个集文化、美景以及旅行打卡目的地等多种钟爱于一身的不可思议的国家。 让我们来告诉您造访秘鲁的原因！ 它的美食！地根据世界旅游奖秘鲁已被视为世界上最好的美食目的，通过不同水果，蔬菜以及鱼类等多变的搭配，其琳琅满目的佳肴提供了不同香味的选择与口感的享受。 CeviChe及其经典菜Ajide de Galina非常受欢迎。让您拿得起放不下的只有筷子！\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-298\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/peru-1-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"peru\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n它的美景！如果您在度假期间希望另辟蹊径，发现不可思议的地方，那么秘鲁就是您的不二选择！ 其中最令人印象深刻的景点是马丘比丘，一个古老的印加城堡，被认为是现代世界十大奇观之一。这是印加人在山上建造的最重要的作品，被精细的雕刻在硕大的巨石上。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-297\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/peru-2-Copy-413x220.jpg\" alt=\"peru\" width=\"413\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n他们的手工艺！如果你是一个喜欢购买旅行纪念品的旅行者，秘鲁的工艺品将会迷惑你的心！ 这些产品，手工制作，当地居民借此完美地代表了他们的艺术，历史和文化。\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:en]Peru is a country that falls in love with the incredible contrasts of its culture, destinations and landscapes. The reasons to visit it are many and here we tell you! Its gastronomy: Peru has been considered the best culinary destination in the world according to the World Travel Awards, thanks to its so rich and diverse cuisine that stands out for the combination of fruits, vegetables and fish, offering many options of aromas and flavors to enjoy. Ceviche and its typical dish known as ají de gallina, are very popular. You can not stop trying them!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-298\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/peru-1-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"peru\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nHis landscapes: If what you are looking for during your vacations is to change the environment and discover incredible places, Peru is your destination! One of its most impressive attractions is the Machu Picchu, an ancient Inca citadel considered one of the ten wonders of the modern world. This is the most important work for the Incas, built on a mountain, based on stones that were carved with great precision and detail.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-297\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/peru-2-Copy-413x220.jpg\" alt=\"peru\" width=\"413\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nTheir crafts: If you are one of the travelers that enjoys buying souvenirs of your trip, the crafts of Peru will enchant you! These products, handmade by their inhabitants, perfectly represent their art, history and culture.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-296\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/peru-3-Copy-331x220.jpg\" alt=\"peru\" width=\"331\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nAre you already convinced? Know the best options to travel to Peru here -&gt;\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:]', '[:zh]将秘鲁加入您下一次旅游目的地的原因？[:en]Why should you include Peru in your next vacation?[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'why-should-you-include-peru-in-your-next-vacation', '', '', '2018-08-16 20:48:13', '2018-08-16 20:48:13', '', 0, 'https://anditrip.com/?p=295', 0, 'post', '', 0),
