(324, 1, '2018-08-08 21:00:58', '2018-08-08 21:00:58', '[:zh]一个无与伦比且令人难以置信的区域，在那里您可以发现文化、自然、历史的广泛性以及美食和景观的多样性。 在拉丁美洲、探险精神是永无止境的！\r\n\r\n1，你可以探索古老并具有千年历史的城市，领略先于西班牙人到来之前并统治了很多年的早期文明产物。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-308\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/latinamerica-1-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"latinamerica\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n2，你将有机会浏览世界上最大、最令人印象深刻、最深、最宽的河流：亚马逊河。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-309\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/latinamerica-2-Copy-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"latinamerica\" width=\"391\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n3，你可以品尝到被许多人认为是世界上最好的哥伦比亚咖啡，这得益于它的质量和真实的味道\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-305\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/latinamerica-3-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"latinamerica\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n4，您将享受到丰富的异国情调美食，从秘鲁的Cevche，到可口的哥伦比亚Paosa。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-304\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/latinamerica-4-Copy-289x220.jpg\" alt=\"latinamerica\" width=\"289\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n想拥有独道的体验吗？我们有可以满足您的所有计划 -&gt;\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:en]A region of incredible contrasts, where you find a wide cultural, natural, historical, gastronomic and landscape diversity. In Latin America, the adventures are endless! 1. You can explore ancient and millenary cities, fruit of the civilizations that reigned for years before the arrival of the Spanish.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-308\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/latinamerica-1-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"latinamerica\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n2- You will have the opportunity to navigate the largest, most impressive, deepest and widest river in the world: the Amazon.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-309\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/latinamerica-2-Copy-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"latinamerica\" width=\"391\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n3- You can taste Colombian coffee, considered by many to be the best in the world, thanks to its quality and authentic flavor.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-305\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/latinamerica-3-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"latinamerica\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n4- You will enjoy a rich and exotic gastronomy that goes from the Peruvian ceviche, to the delicious Colombian paisa tray.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-304\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/latinamerica-4-Copy-289x220.jpg\" alt=\"latinamerica\" width=\"289\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nDo you want to live unique experiences? Meet all our plans here -&gt;\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:]', '[:zh]拉丁美洲，一个为您带来“丰富”的地区[:en]Latin America, a region that has a lot to offer you.[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'latin-america-a-region-that-has-a-lot-to-offer-you', '', '', '2018-08-16 20:45:56', '2018-08-16 20:45:56', '', 0, 'https://anditrip.com/?p=324', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(326, 1, '2018-08-08 21:13:21', '2018-08-08 21:13:21', '[:zh]这个哥伦比亚的首都城市聚焦并融入了夜生活，博物馆，文化层次的多样性等特征。在这个全年平均气温14摄氏度的城市里，嬉戏于现代化殖民建筑群使其成为这个国家到访人数最多的旅游目的地。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-310\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bogota-1-329x220.jpg\" alt=\"bogota\" width=\"329\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n梦赛特拉教堂是这座城市的主要主打景点之一。您可以通过绳索、缆车、徒步到达并找到遗失的圣殿，在那里一边欣赏美妙的风景，一边享受哥伦比亚食物的美味以及手工艺品等传统工艺的熏陶。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-319\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bogota-2-Copy-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"bogota\" width=\"391\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n另一方面，在拉坎德拉里亚的历史中心，有一些重要的博物馆，在那里你可以欣赏博特罗和毕加索的绘画，那些令人屏息的黄金碎片的记忆。 在这一地区，你还可以参观1539建造的柏辽广场，周围有重要的公共建筑、旅游景点和历史景点。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-318\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bogota-3-Copy-329x220.jpg\" alt=\"bogota\" width=\"329\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n商业区提供了关于服装店，鞋类，配件，珠宝，技术，古董和工艺品的 丰富选择，为您带来难以忘怀的哥伦比亚最佳回忆。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-317\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bogota-4-Copy-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"bogota\" width=\"391\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n您还可以找到著名的佐纳G区，它是博格达市的专属，同时也已成为游客最热衷的地方之一。大家喜欢在此享受各种各样的菜肴，因为它有令人眼花缭乱的餐厅。 准备好走进并感受这座城市魅力的你，可以点击此处了解更多-&gt;\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:en]The Colombian capital is a city with a lot to offer, its cultural diversity, nightlife, museums, its pleasant average temperature of 14 ° C and its modern and colonial buildings, make it one of the most visited destinations in the country.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-310\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bogota-1-329x220.jpg\" alt=\"bogota\" width=\"329\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nThe Cerro de Monserrate is one of the main attractions of the city, which can be climbed by funicular, cable car or walking, above you can find the Sanctuary of the fallen Lord, the viewpoint that offers a wonderful view, restaurants of Colombian food and sale of crafts and typical products.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-319\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bogota-2-Copy-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"391\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nOn the other hand, in the Historic Center of La Candelaria, there are important museums, where you can admire paintings by Botero and Picasso, as well as incredible pieces of gold. In this area, you can also visit the Plaza de Bolívar, built since 1539 and which is surrounded by important public buildings and tourist and historical points of interest.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-318\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bogota-3-Copy-329x220.jpg\" alt=\"bogota\" width=\"329\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nIts commercial area offers a wide variety of options in clothing stores, footwear, accessories, jewelry, technology, antiques and crafts, to bring your best memory of Colombia.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-317\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bogota-4-Copy-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"boogota\" width=\"391\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nYou will also find the famous Zona G, which is one of the most exclusive in the city and has become the favorite place for travelers looking to enjoy a wide variety of cuisine, as it has a large number of restaurants of all kinds. Image 5 And you, when are you coming to enjoy this city charm? Know all your travel options here -&gt;\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:]', '[:zh]博格达，一个不容错过的旅游目的地[:en]Bogotá, a destination you can not miss![:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bogota-a-destinationyou-can-not-miss', '', '', '2018-08-16 20:38:48', '2018-08-16 20:38:48', '', 0, 'https://anditrip.com/?p=326', 0, 'post', '', 0),
