(330, 1, '2018-08-09 13:28:07', '2018-08-09 13:28:07', '[:zh]这座城堡是最富盛名的考古中心之一，同时又在颇具声望的世界旅游大奖上斩获“2017年最佳旅游景观”大奖。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-315\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/machupichu-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"machupichu\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n它被称为印加人的珠宝和杰作，锻造了世界上最重要的文化之一。这个地方有一种无与伦比的美，被山上的森林包围着，既有自然环境的威严又有致命的历史吸引力，保留了早前西班牙文明的历史轨迹。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-321\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/machupichu2-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"machupichu\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n想要拥有一个不二的体验？ 点击此处设计您的行程-&gt;\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:en]This citadel is one of the most famous archaeological centers and was chosen as \"Best tourist attraction in the world 2017\" in the prestigious World Travel Awards.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-315\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/machupichu-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"machupichu\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nIt is known as the jewel and masterpiece of the Incas, who forged one of the most important cultures that have existed in the world. This place has an incomparable beauty and is surrounded by the forests of the mountains, offering the perfect combination between the majesty of its natural settings and the attractiveness of its history and the pre-Hispanic remains it has.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-321\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/machupichu2-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"machupichu\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nWould you like to live a unique experience? Schedule your trip here -&gt;\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:]', '[:zh]麦德林，南美洲最佳旅游目的地[:en]One of the 7 wonders, come to Machu Picchu![:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'one-of-the-7-wonders-come-to-machu-picchu', '', '', '2018-08-13 19:30:59', '2018-08-13 19:30:59', '', 0, 'https://anditrip.com/?p=330', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(333, 1, '2018-08-09 14:08:11', '2018-08-09 14:08:11', '[:zh]麦德林是一个充满鲜花、色彩、风味和创新的旅游目的地，已经成为成千上万的游客喜爱的城市，并已经在TripAdvisor平台上被它列为南美洲最好的旅游目的地城市，并使它当之无愧的斩获了“旅行者选择”奖。 过去殖民地与现在城市创新间的融会贯通，使之成为世界公认的旅游胜地。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-314\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/medellin-1-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"medellin\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n它被誉为“永恒之春城”，因其宜人的平均气温（24°C）以及其著名的花卉交易会、花园、公园以及环绕它的山地景观而得名。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-313\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/medellin-2-Copy-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"medellin\" width=\"391\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n麦德林随时准备为游客带来惊喜！不容错过的参观，计划你的旅行吧-&gt;\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:en]Medellin is a destination full of flowers, colors, flavors and innovation and has become the favorite city of thousands of tourists who have cataloged it on the TripAdvisor platform as the best tourist destination in South America, making it worthy of the \"Traveler\'s Choice\" award. The mixture between the colonial past and the innovativeness of the city, makes it a tourist attraction recognized worldwide.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-314\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/medellin-1-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"medellin\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nIt is known as the \"city of eternal spring\" thanks to its pleasant average climate of 24 ° C, its famous flower fair, gardens, parks and the mountain landscapes that surround it.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-313\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/medellin-2-Copy-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"medellin\" width=\"391\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nMedellin is always ready to surprise its visitors! Do not miss visiting it and plan your trip here -&gt;\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:]', '[:zh]麦德林，南美洲最佳旅游目的地[:en]Discover Medellin, the best tourist destination in South America[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'english-discover-medellin-the-best-tourist-destination-in-south-america', '', '', '2018-08-18 06:25:13', '2018-08-18 06:25:13', '', 0, 'https://anditrip.com/?p=333', 0, 'post', '', 0),
