(346, 1, '2018-08-10 13:12:33', '2018-08-10 13:12:33', '[:zh][:zh]科科拉 山 谷是一 个美丽 的自然景 观，位于哥 伦比亚Quindío山脉以及安第斯山脉中央山脉的山谷中，是咖啡区最杰出的旅游胜地之一。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-312\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cocora-1-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"valle cocora\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n它以奇特的绿色山脉和繁茂的植被著称，在这里被发现的哥伦比亚国家树“拉帕尔马德塞拉”，高达60米，遍布整个山群。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-320\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cocora-2-Copy-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"vlle cocora\" width=\"293\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nOrejiamarillos鹦鹉以及其他濒危动物在这些树上生活并繁殖。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-311\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cocora-3-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"valle cocora\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n毫无疑问，科科拉山谷是山脉、动物群、棕榈树、河流、雾和大自然的完美结合…不要错过去了解它的机会-&gt;\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:en]The Cocora Valley is a beautiful natural landscape located in a mountainous valley of the Central Cordillera of the Colombian Andes in the department of Quindío and is one of the most outstanding tourist destinations in the Coffee Region.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-312\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cocora-1-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"valle cocora\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nIt is distinguished by its fantastic view of green mountains and exuberant vegetation, where the national tree of Colombia \"la Palma de Cera\" is found, which with its imposing height of up to 60 meters, adorns the whole landscape.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-320\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cocora-2-Copy-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"vlle cocora\" width=\"293\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nOrejiamarillos parrots live and feed on these trees, as well as other species of animals that are in danger of extinction.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-311\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cocora-3-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"valle cocora\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nDefinitely, the Cocora Valley is mountains, fauna, palm trees, rivers, fog and nature ... Do not miss the opportunity to get to know it! Know your travel options here -&gt;\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:][:en]The Cocora Valley is a beautiful natural landscape located in a mountainous valley of the Central Cordillera of the Colombian Andes in the department of Quindío and is one of the most outstanding tourist destinations in the Coffee Region.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-312\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cocora-1-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"valle cocora\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nIt is distinguished by its fantastic view of green mountains and exuberant vegetation, where the national tree of Colombia \"la Palma de Cera\" is found, which with its imposing height of up to 60 meters, adorns the whole landscape.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-320\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cocora-2-Copy-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"vlle cocora\" width=\"293\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nOrejiamarillos parrots live and feed on these trees, as well as other species of animals that are in danger of extinction.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-311\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/cocora-3-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"valle cocora\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nDefinitely, the Cocora Valley is mountains, fauna, palm trees, rivers, fog and nature ... Do not miss the opportunity to get to know it! Know your travel options here -&gt;\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:]', '[:zh]科科 拉  山 谷，一个自 然旅行 爱好者的理想的目的地[:en]The Cocora Valley, an ideal destination for nature lovers.[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-cocora-valley-an-ideal-destination-for-nature-lovers', '', '', '2018-08-16 20:58:44', '2018-08-16 20:58:44', '', 0, 'https://anditrip.com/?p=346', 0, 'post', '', 0);
