(349, 1, '2018-08-10 15:50:20', '2018-08-10 15:50:20', '[:zh]该国位于南美洲大陆西北部，拥有丰富多选的旅游目的地，同时具有富饶的自然、文化和历史资源 让我们来告诉您4个选择哥伦比亚所谓您下一个旅游目的地的原因\r\n\r\n1，人的魅力 作为世界上最幸福的国家之一，哥伦比亚人的生活充满了欢乐的气氛，它的居民有各种各样的特征、种族、口音，并且总是对每一个访问他们土地的人微笑。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-356\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/colombia-1-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"colombia\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n2，气候与景观 这里的温度和风景一样丰富多变，在那里你可以找到现代和殖民城市，找到自然森林、稀树草原、沙漠、湿地、帕拉莫斯和世界上最大的河流，亚马孙河。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-357\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/colombia-2-Copy-332x220.jpg\" alt=\"colombia\" width=\"332\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n3，它的建筑结构 在这个国家，一切都是美丽的、多样的。在它的建筑中，你可以发现像麦德林和波哥大一样的建筑，也可以领略到充满历史和殖民魅力的建筑，如卡塔赫纳\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-358\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/colombia-3-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"colombia\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n4，您的咖啡 哥伦比亚以其风味和品质而闻名于世，是世界上生产软咖啡的最主要国家之一。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-359\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/colombia-4-Copy-331x220.jpg\" alt=\"colombia\" width=\"331\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n如果您已具备来到哥伦比亚的足够理由？欢迎点击此处获取详情-&gt;\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:en]This country located northwest of the continent of South America, has a wide variety of tourist destinations rich in nature, culture and history. Here we tell you 4 great reasons why you should include Colombia in your next vacation -&gt; 1. The charisma of its people. Being one of the happiest countries in the world, Colombians live full of joy that spreads, its inhabitants have a mixture of traits, races, accents and always receive a smile to everyone who visits their land.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-356\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/colombia-1-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"colombia\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n2. The climate and its landscapes. Here the temperatures are as diverse as the landscapes, where you can find from modern and colonial cities, to natural forests, savannas, deserts, wetlands, páramos and the largest river in the world, the Amazon.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-357\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/colombia-2-Copy-332x220.jpg\" alt=\"colombia\" width=\"332\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n3. Its architecture. In this country everything is beautiful and varied, in its architecture you can see from buildings and innovative structures such as Medellin and Bogota, to facades full of history and colonial charm such as Cartagena.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-358\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/colombia-3-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"colombia\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n4- Your coffee. Famous for its flavor and quality, Colombia is positioned among the main countries producing soft coffee in the world. Its coffee landscapes were declared a World Heritage Site by Unesco and offer a unique combination of its culture and tradition.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-359\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/colombia-4-Copy-331x220.jpg\" alt=\"colombia\" width=\"331\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nYou already have enough reasons to come to Colombia! Know all our travel options here -&gt;\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:]', '[:zh]一个 充 满 风味 的 国家[:en]Colombia, a country full of flavor.[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'colombia-a-country-full-of-flavor', '', '', '2018-10-03 14:04:07', '2018-10-03 14:04:07', '', 0, 'https://anditrip.com/?p=349', 0, 'post', '', 0),
