我该怎么办？</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n首先，您必须向付款时注册的电子邮件帐户发送确认交易的电子邮件，如果您尚未收到，则必须联系Natalia Sanchez确认交易状态。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>8.如果我没有收到付款证明怎么办？</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n对于通过付款地点批准的每笔交易，您将在付款时指明的电子邮件地址收到购买参考的付款证明。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n如果您没有收到，可以联系Natalia Sanchez或发送电子邮件或发送电子邮件至info@anditrip.com，要求将优惠券退回到付款时注册的同一电子邮件地址。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<div class=\"contenido-1\" style=\"width: 100%; padding: 0 100px; box-shadow: 0px 5px 5px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0px 8px 10px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14), 0px 3px 14px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);\">\r\n\r\n<!--<?php the_content(); ?>-->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>[:en]<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<div class=\"contenido-1\" style=\"width: 100%; padding: 0 100px; box-shadow: 0px 5px 5px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0px 8px 10px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14), 0px 3px 14px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);\">\r\n<h2 class=\"separacion separacion_top\"></h2>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h2 class=\"separacion \" style=\"padding-top: 2em;\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-418\" style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/6070773-e1535041744583.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"59\" /></h2>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">1. ¿What is Place to pay<span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">?</span></span></span></strong></h4>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; padding: 30px 0px;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Place to pay is the Platform of Electronic Payments That ANDITRIP, S.A uses to Process Online Transactions generated into the Virtual Store with the forms of payment enabled for this purpose.</span></p>\r\n<span class=\"p-r-q\" style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: 80