o Pay Place to pay also has the constant monitoring of McAfee Secure and the signature of electronic messages with Certicamara.</p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: 800; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 4. ¿Can I perform the purchase any day and time? </span></span></span>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #333; text-align: justify; padding: 30px 0px;\">Yes, at <strong>ANDITRIP, S.A</strong>, your purchases are made online, 7 days a week, 24 hours a day, just a click away.</p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: 800; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">5. ¿Can I change the payment method?</span></span></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333333; font-size: 16px;\">If you have not yet finalized your payment, you will have to return to the initial step and choose the payment method you prefer. Once the purchase is finished it is not possible to change the payment method</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333333; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>ANDITRIP, S.A:</strong> the previous point applies to the form of payment, but accepts the return policies that the store has to comply with Article 51 of the Consumer Statute Law.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: 800; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 6. ¿Paying electronically has some value for me as a buyer? </span></span></span>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #333; text-align: justify; padding: 30px 0px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000d6; font-weight: 800;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Yes, in No, the electronic payments made through Place to Pay not charged additional to the buyer.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: 800; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 7. ¿What should I do if my transaction did not end?</span></span></span>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #333; text-align: justify; padding: 30px 0px;\">In the first instance, you must send an email confirming the transaction to the email account registered at the time of payment, if you have not received it, you must contact Natalia Sanchez to confirm the status of the transaction.</p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: 800; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 8. ¿What should I do if I did not receive proof of payment?</span></span></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333333; font-size: 16px;\">For each transaction approved through Place to Pay, you will receive a proof of payment with the purchase reference at the email address you indicated at the time of payment.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333333; font-size: 16px;\">If you do not receive it, you can contact Natalia Sanchez or the e-mail or email to info@anditrip.com, to request the return of the voucher to the same e-mail address registered at the time of payment.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>[:]', 'FAQS', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'faqs', '', '', '2018-08-30 14:48:25', '2018-08-30 14:48:25', '', 0, 'https://anditrip.com/?page_id=391', 0, 'page', '', 0),
