(490, 1, '2018-09-04 14:32:42', '2018-09-04 14:32:42', '[:zh]音乐传递情感，旋律唤醒快乐的感觉，甚至悲伤，在和谐的声音中，你可以欣赏一个国家丰富的文化、每个地方的传统以及理解发现文化与文化之间是有多么的不同。另外，去这些南美的音乐国度旅游就像带着所有情感去旅行，但最重要的是旋律所带来的体验。\r\n\r\n探索阿根廷性感的探戈节奏 ：探戈是阿根廷的标志，是一种有着性感动作与身形的复杂舞蹈，是一个让夫妻俩一刻也不松开对方的手的地方。尽管它发源于城市郊区，在那里，人们用抒情歌词来淹没悲伤，随着时间的推移，逐渐演变成所有人的音乐。\r\n\r\n布宜诺斯艾利斯目前已经有约200个跳舞或是观看探戈秀的地方，喜欢这类舞蹈的人有机会在这些地方跳舞、欣赏音乐以及学习，伴随着不同的环境和特色。在8月，阿根廷的首都是节日和阿根廷世界冠军赛的举办地，人们跳着milongas（探戈的一种）欢庆，还有公共音乐会举办。你敢于前来探索探戈的性感节奏吗？\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-487\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Imagen-1-Copy-1-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"tango\" width=\"391\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n巴西的桑巴舞蹈节奏：巴西是拉美游客最多的地方之一，一个非常有趣和快乐的地方，充满着派对、风俗和舞蹈。在这里，音乐在国内的流行文化中占据着非常重要的地位，桑巴是巴西人的标志。它有着混合着非洲和当地节奏的旋律，并逐渐成为了全国的象征。\r\n桑巴也是这个国家最激烈的音乐表达方式，如果你打算在任意时间前往巴西，你将不可避免的加入这些节庆，在美妙的桑巴节奏中体验独一无二又难以忘怀的经历。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-488\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Imagen-2-Copy-1-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"samba\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n卡利，哥伦比亚的萨尔萨舞之都：萨尔萨是一种代表和识别卡利的音乐节奏，它的声音、舞者和音乐流派历史正标志着这个地方区。卡利以世界萨尔萨之都闻名，并且毫不逊色于这个称号，在城市里你可以欣赏到非常棒的萨尔萨表演，你还可以学习如何去跳它。在这里有超过90家舞蹈学校和约115家主题场所，它们被誉为老式俱乐部，在那里这种音乐流派的老歌将会带你回到过去，在salsotecas，定音鼓的节奏和小号的声音在耳边缭绕。\r\n\r\n去卡利旅行，是不可能不被这里的节奏所引诱的，萨尔萨是这里的旅游产品，并成为了全世界游客的最爱。不要远远的观望这里，大胆的随着萨尔萨的节奏舞动你的臀部吧！\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-489\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Imagen-3-Copy-1-332x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"332\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:en]Music transmits emotions, melodies awaken sensations of joy, joy and even sadness, with sounds in harmony you can appreciate the cultural richness of a country, the traditions of each place, but also understand and observe how different a culture of culture can be. other. Travel to these musical places of South America and travel with all the senses, but above all the hearing, the melodies and experiences they offer.\r\n\r\nExplore the sensual rhythms of Tango in Argentina: Tango is a symbol of Argentina, it is a complex dance with sensual figures and movements, where the couple does not let go for a single moment. Although its beginnings were in the suburbs of the city, where people drowned their sorrows with sweeping lyrics over time evolved and became the music of all.\r\n\r\nBuenos Aires currently has approximately 200 places where you can dance or witness tango shows, who like this genre and dance has the possibility to dance, listen and learn in many places with different environments and characteristics. During the month of August the capital of Argentina is the headquarters of the Festival and World Tango Championship, with popular milongas and public concerts. Do you dare to explore the sensual rhythms of tango?\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-487\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Imagen-1-Copy-1-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"cali\" width=\"391\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nBrazil dances to the rhythm of the Samba: This country is one of the most visited in Latin America, a very fun, happy place, full of parties, customs and dances, where music is very important in the popular culture of the country, being the samba the symbol of Brazilian identity. A genre whose melody is the mixture of African rhythms with the locals until it became a national icon.\r\n\r\nIt is the maximum musical expression of the country and if you visit Brazil any time of the year, it will be inevitable not to join the festivities and at the best rhythm of the samba to live a unique and unforgettable experience\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-488\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Imagen-2-Copy-1-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"cali\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nCali, the capital of Salsa in Colombia: Salsa is the musical rhythm that represents and identifies the city of Cali, the sound, dancers and the history of this musical genre culturally marks the region. Cali is known as the World Capital of Salsa and it is not for less, in the city you can see great salsa shows, you will learn to dance this musical rhythm, there are more than 90 dance schools and about 115 thematic establishments, known as old-fashioned clubs where the oldest songs of this genre will transport you to the past and the salsotecas where the timpani rhythm and the trumpets do not stop sounding.\r\n\r\nVisiting Cali and not being seduced by this rhythm is impossible, salsa is a tourist product of the region and this has made it a favorite destination for many travelers in the world. Do not overlook this destiny and dare to move your hips to the rhythm of salsa!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-489\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Imagen-3-Copy-1-332x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"332\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:]', '[:zh]充满音乐和乐趣的地方[:en]Destinations with lots of music and fun.[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e5%85%85%e6%bb%a1%e9%9f%b3%e4%b9%90%e5%92%8c%e4%b9%90%e8%b6%a3%e7%9a%84%e5%9c%b0%e6%96%b9', '', '', '2018-09-04 14:32:42', '2018-09-04 14:32:42', '', 0, 'https://anditrip.com/?p=490', 0, 'post', '', 0),
