(503, 1, '2018-09-04 15:08:20', '2018-09-04 15:08:20', '[:zh]亚马逊是世界上最大的热带雨林，它围绕着亚马逊河流域，一个5500000平方千米的地区，被巴西、秘鲁、哥伦比亚、玻利维亚、厄瓜多尔、圭亚那、委内瑞拉和苏里南共同拥有，它们都是这片土地的第一批居民。亚马逊丛林充满着魅力、异国情调的物种、迷人的风光和冒险，如果你打算游览南美，你一定要住在这里。\r\n\r\n亚马逊有着不可比拟的生物多样性，世界上最丰富的地区之一，有着参天大树的森林，高到可以遮住你的视野，还容纳了3000种可食用的水果，此外，还有很多有医用价值的植物和各种野生花朵，用独特的美和吸引着你。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-498\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Imagen-1-Copy-3-321x220.jpg\" alt=\"amazon\" width=\"321\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n这里的动物群令人惊叹，种类繁多，包含2500种鱼类，比如亚马逊的灰海豚和粉海豚，这里也是食人鱼的故乡。这丛林里你可以看到上千种鸟类，它们有着五彩缤纷的羽毛，为风景添色；上百万中昆虫，数百种哺乳动物，比如伶猴属，这是一种有着柔软和丝滑毛发的小型动物，然而目前大部分物种都面临着威胁，因为它们的居住地正在被破坏。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-499\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Imagen-2-Copy-3-331x220.jpg\" alt=\"amazon\" width=\"331\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n亚马逊不仅是世界上最大的森林，也是土著居民的祖居。在这里有很多不同种族的土著，大约有350个种族，他们分散在不同的部落里，每个部落都有自己的语言和文化。有些部落从未接触过外界的文明。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-500\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Imagen-3-Copy-3-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"amazon\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n在亚马逊你可以享受远足，深入丛林，去了解拜访不同种族的当地人、他们的文化和传统，在这片绿色的天堂里，你可以欣赏繁盛的风景，也可以探索亚马逊河。这里是一个生态旅游和冒险爱好者的理想之地。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-502\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Imagen-4-Copy-2-331x220.jpg\" alt=\"amazon\" width=\"331\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:en]It is the largest tropical forest in the world that surrounds the Amazon River basin, an area of ​​5,500,000 km2 that is shared by Brazil, Peru, Colombia, Bolivia, Ecuador, Guyana, Venezuela and Suriname, both being the first where most of the territory is located. The Amazon is full of charms, exotic species, captivating landscapes and adventures that you must live when you plan to visit South America.\r\n\r\nThe Amazon has an incomparable biodiversity and one of the richest in the world, has forests with incredible trees, so high that you will lose sight of them, also houses some 3000 species of fruits and all are edible, in addition there are many species of medicinal plants and variety of wild flowers that captivate you with their unique beauty and colorful\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-498\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Imagen-1-Copy-3-321x220.jpg\" alt=\"amazon\" width=\"321\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nIts fauna is amazing and varied, which includes 2500 types of fish, like the gray and pink dolphins of the Amazon, it is also the home of piranhas. In this jungle you will observe thousands of species of birds that adorn the landscape with their colorful plumage, millions of insects, hundreds of mammals, such as the titi monkey, small sized animals with a soft and silky coat, currently the majority of the species are considered threat as a result of the destruction of their habitat.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-499\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Imagen-2-Copy-3-331x220.jpg\" alt=\"amazon\" width=\"331\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nThe Amazon is not only the largest forest on the planet, it is also the ancestral home of indigenous groups. In it there are a variety of natives, with an approximate of 350 ethnic groups scattered in different tribes, each with its own language and culture. Some of them have never had contact with civilization.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-500\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Imagen-3-Copy-3-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"amazon\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nIn the Amazon you can enjoy excursions and go into the jungle to know and visit and visit the different populations of the natives, their culture and traditions, in this green paradise you can admire exuberant landscapes and explore part of the Amazon River. An ideal plan for lovers of ecotourism and adventure sports.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-502\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Imagen-4-Copy-2-331x220.jpg\" alt=\"amazon\" width=\"331\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:]', '[:zh]亚马逊的魅力[:en]The Amazon and its charms[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e4%ba%9a%e9%a9%ac%e9%80%8a%e7%9a%84%e9%ad%85%e5%8a%9b', '', '', '2018-09-04 15:08:20', '2018-09-04 15:08:20', '', 0, 'https://anditrip.com/?p=503', 0, 'post', '', 0),
