(549, 1, '2018-10-03 19:02:16', '2018-10-03 19:02:16', '[:zh]多拉达尔，安蒂奥基亚省的一座小镇，把自己定位为这个国家的探险目的地参考之一。其植物群、动物群以及自然特性的多样性使其可以发展广泛的户外活动项目，并吸引着国内外游客。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-545\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1-doradal-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"Doradal\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n这里有天然瀑布，它的声音环境使我们可以在周围散步，虽然事实上这里也是一个在大自然中心洗澡和放松的理想之地。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-546\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/2-doradal-Copy-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"Doradal\" width=\"391\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n另一方面，在克拉罗自然保护区的峡谷河流处，你可以乘筏或者潜入水中享受水晶般清澈的河水。这是一个充满乐趣的体验，你一定试了还想再来！\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-547\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/3-doradal-Copy-147x220.jpg\" alt=\"Doradal\" width=\"147\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n另外，多拉达尔还拥有很多奢华酒店，可以满足你的全部想象。游泳池、餐厅和美妙的自然环境都将成为你停留在安蒂奥基亚难以忘怀的记忆以及你还想再回来的理由。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-548\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/4-doradal-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"Doradal\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:en]Doradal, this township of Antioquia, has positioned itself as one of the reference adventure destinations of the country. The diversity of its flora, fauna and natural characteristics have helped to develop the wide range of outdoor activities that today attract locals and foreigners.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-545\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1-doradal-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"Doradal\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nIt has natural waterfalls whose sound ambient the walks that can be done in the surroundings, although in fact they are ideal to take a bath and relax in the middle of nature.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-546\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/2-doradal-Copy-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"Doradal\" width=\"391\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nOn the other hand, in the Cañón del Río Claro Natural Reserve it is possible to raft or simply navigate in air rafts for its fast and crystal clear waters. An experience full of fun that you will definitely want to repeat !.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-547\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/3-doradal-Copy-147x220.jpg\" alt=\"Doradal\" width=\"147\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nIn addition, Doradal is host to a wide range of luxury hotels that include all the comforts you can imagine. Pools, restaurants and spectacular natural environments that will be the scene of an unforgettable stay in this part of Antioquia to which you will want to return\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-548\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/4-doradal-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"Doradal\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:]', '[:zh]游览充满冒险与乐趣的多拉达尔[:en]Visit full of adventure and fun at Doradal[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e6%b8%b8%e8%a7%88%e5%85%85%e6%bb%a1%e5%86%92%e9%99%a9%e4%b8%8e%e4%b9%90%e8%b6%a3%e7%9a%84%e5%a4%9a%e6%8b%89%e8%be%be%e5%b0%94', '', '', '2018-10-03 19:02:16', '2018-10-03 19:02:16', '', 0, 'https://anditrip.com/?p=549', 0, 'post', '', 0),
