(554, 1, '2018-10-03 19:16:09', '2018-10-03 19:16:09', '[:zh]这里是哥伦比亚著名的塑料艺术家Fernando Botero的摇篮，麦德林是热爱艺术、创新和享受舒适的山地气候的人们的天堂。了解更多关于哥伦比亚永恒之春的城市。\r\n\r\n目前，这里有197个拥有者24小时免费网络的区域，这使得麦德林成为了与全国联系最紧密的城市。这里有最完善和有效率的公共交通系统，使得出行快速又方便。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-551\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1-medellín-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"medellin\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n在众多景点中，位于城市中心的安蒂奥基亚博物馆拥有着国内外参考性的艺术收藏，包括前哥伦比亚时期的艺术和陶瓷，全年都吸引着国内外的游客。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-552\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/2-medellín-Copy-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"medellin\" width=\"391\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nBotero广场是一个不可缺少的城市代表地，由于这里可以看到这位艺术家的23个雕塑，分散在7000平米的建筑中。这里可以免费进入，并且展览将永远存在，久而久之成为了一个汇合点与当地的骄傲。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-553\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/3-medellín-Copy-383x220.jpeg\" alt=\"medellin\" width=\"383\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:en]Cradle of Fernando Botero, famed Colombian plastic artist, Medellín stands out as the ideal destination for people who appreciate art, innovation and also enjoy the pleasant mountain climate. Learn a little more about the city of the eternal spring of Colombia.\r\n\r\nCurrently, it has 197 zones with free internet connection 24/7, which makes it the most connected city in the whole country. It has the most complete and efficient public transport system, which makes moving around it fast and easy.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-551\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1-medellín-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"medellin\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nAmong its attractions, the Museum of Antioquia, located in the center of the city, contains artistic collections of national and international reference, including pre-Columbian art and ceramics, which attracts national and foreign tourists throughout the year.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-552\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/2-medellín-Copy-391x220.jpg\" alt=\"medellin\" width=\"391\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nThe Plaza Botero is an indispensable reference of the city, since it can be seen 23 sculptures of this artist, distributed in the 7000 square meters that compose it. Being of free access and permanent exhibition, it has become a meeting point and local pride.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-553\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/3-medellín-Copy-383x220.jpeg\" alt=\"medellin\" width=\"383\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:]', '[:zh]麦德林，哥伦比亚的创新之都[:en]Medellín, the city of innovation in Colombia[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e9%ba%a6%e5%be%b7%e6%9e%97%ef%bc%8c%e5%93%a5%e4%bc%a6%e6%af%94%e4%ba%9a%e7%9a%84%e5%88%9b%e6%96%b0%e4%b9%8b%e9%83%bd', '', '', '2018-10-03 19:16:09', '2018-10-03 19:16:09', '', 0, 'https://anditrip.com/?p=554', 0, 'post', '', 0),
