(563, 1, '2018-10-05 15:38:30', '2018-10-05 15:38:30', '[:zh]也许甘蔗作物是这个城市的特点，对当地人们的快乐起着作用，但是说到卡利，就是在说加勒比节的经典节奏：萨尔萨。\r\n\r\n在1536年成立，被誉为天堂的分支，卡利是哥伦比亚的第三大城市以及全国主要的城市、经济和工业中心之一。近年来，这个城市这座城市沿着河岸发展，为当地人和外国人提供各种各样的旅游产品和服务。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-556\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1-Cali-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"Cali\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n为了体验卡利所有的辉煌，有一些事你不得不做，那就是跳萨尔萨舞。当你看到当地舞者的技巧时不要感到害怕，当游览这座城市时，你将找到学习舞步的不同选择，不要犹豫，立即加入派对吧。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-557\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/2.-cali-Copy-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"Cali\" width=\"293\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n卡利是一个完完全全的旅游地，拥有很多不容错过的处历史价值，例如Hermitage教堂或者建于1747年的San Antonio教堂。另外，Cauca山谷的经典美食融合了西班牙、非洲和土著口味，让你不会后悔品尝这一道美食。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-558\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/3.cali-Copy-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"Cali\" width=\"293\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:en]Maybe the sugarcane crops that characterize this city, have to do with the joy of its people, but talking about Cali is talking about the typical rhythm of the Caribbean fiesta: Salsa.\r\n\r\nFounded in the year 1536 and known as the branch of heaven, Cali is the third city in Colombia and one of the main urban, economic and industrial centers of the country. In recent years this city has developed on the banks of its river to offer a wide range of tourism products and services to locals and foreigners alike.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-556\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1-Cali-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"Cali\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nTo live the Cali experience in all its splendor there is something you can not stop doing, and it is salsa dancing. Do not feel intimidated when you see the skill of the local dancers, when visiting the city you will find multiple options to learn some dance steps and join without hesitation to the party.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-557\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/2.-cali-Copy-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"Cali\" width=\"293\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nCali is a complete tourist destination, with several sites of historical value that you can not miss, such as the Hermitage Church or the Chapel of San Antonio, built in 1747. In addition, the typical cuisine of Valle del Cauca is a fusion of Spanish flavors, African and indigenous, which gave rise to delicious dishes that you will not regret trying.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-558\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/3.cali-Copy-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"Cali\" width=\"293\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:]', '[:zh]全年不休的派对氛围？只在卡利[:en]Festive atmosphere all year round? Only in Cali[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e5%85%a8%e5%b9%b4%e4%b8%8d%e4%bc%91%e7%9a%84%e6%b4%be%e5%af%b9%e6%b0%9b%e5%9b%b4%ef%bc%9f%e5%8f%aa%e5%9c%a8%e5%8d%a1%e5%88%a9', '', '', '2018-10-05 15:38:30', '2018-10-05 15:38:30', '', 0, 'https://anditrip.com/?p=563', 0, 'post', '', 0),
