(573, 1, '2018-11-05 14:17:13', '2018-11-05 14:17:13', '[:zh]圣保罗是巴西主要的经济中心以及拉美的文化中心。\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n大约有46个文化中心，101个博物馆和141个图书馆，构成了圣保罗巨大的文化资源，同时，还有丰富的艺术环境、世界一流的餐厅和奢华的酒店共存，使这里成为了一个不必去嫉妒其他大洲的重要城市的地方。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-570\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-1-Copy-342x220.jpg\" alt=\"Sao paolo\" width=\"342\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n美食是这个势不可挡的城市的主角。除国际化和当地的餐厅，当谈及美食，频繁的食品交易会和移动餐车也是当地人和外国人选择的一部分\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-569\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-2-Copy-165x220.jpg\" alt=\"sao paolo food\" width=\"165\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n圣保罗是南半球最大的城市，同时，也是巴西最大的城市，这里的发展令人晕眩，但并没有因为这个原因，就失去了吸引人的户外娱乐空间和与自然的接触。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-571\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-3-Copy-440x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n这里有111个公园，分散于整座城市，除了动物园和水族馆，这些是圣保罗人和外国人不得不去的娱乐地点。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-572\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-4-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n你想了解这座生机勃勃的城市吗？访问我们的官网，了解更多有关这座拉美城市的信息-&gt; <a href=\"http://www.anditrip.com\">www.anditrip.com</a>[:en]Sao Paulo is the main economic center of Brazil and a great cultural center of Latin America.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nAround 46 cultural centers, 101 museums and 141 libraries make up the vast cultural offer that can be found in Sao Paulo, where together, with a lush artistic environment, world-class restaurants and luxurious hotels coexist, making it a destination that has nothing to envy for important cities in other continents.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-570 size-medium\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-1-Copy-342x220.jpg\" alt=\"Brazil\" width=\"342\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nGastronomy is the protagonist in this unstoppable city. In addition to international and local restaurants, the recurring food fairs and food trucks are part of the options enjoyed by locals and foreigners, when it comes to delicious food.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-569 size-medium\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-2-Copy-165x220.jpg\" alt=\"Brazil\" width=\"165\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nSao Paulo is the largest city in the southern hemisphere and, therefore, the largest city in Brazil, where the development has been vertiginous, but not for that reason, it stops having attractive spaces for outdoor recreation and encounter with nature.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-571 size-medium\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-3-Copy-440x220.jpg\" alt=\"Brazil\" width=\"440\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nIt has 111 parks distributed throughout the city, in addition to the zoo and aquarium, those are the alternatives that the Paulists and foreigners have to spend different moments of recreation.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-572 size-medium\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-4-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"Brazil\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nDo you want to know this exuberant city? Enter our website and learn more about this destination in Latin America -&gt; <a href=\"http://www.anditrip.com\">www.anditrip.com</a>[:]', '[:zh]圣保罗，最具国际化的城市[:en]Sao Paulo, the most cosmopolitan city[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e5%9c%a3%e4%bf%9d%e7%bd%97%ef%bc%8c%e6%9c%80%e5%85%b7%e5%9b%bd%e9%99%85%e5%8c%96%e7%9a%84%e5%9f%8e%e5%b8%82', '', '', '2018-11-05 14:27:07', '2018-11-05 14:27:07', '', 0, 'https://anditrip.com/?p=573', 0, 'post', '', 0),
