(579, 1, '2018-11-05 14:47:38', '2018-11-05 14:47:38', '[:zh]<!--more-->\r\n\r\n你将会铭记一生的风景\r\n\r\n同时也被誉为太平洋的珍珠，瓦尔帕莱索拥有着各种各样的文化活动和美丽的餐厅，在这里你永远不会感到无聊。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-582\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-1-Copy-1-339x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"339\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n选择之一是去参观瓦尔帕莱索自然离世博物馆，那里有着广泛种类的植物群和动物群，是这个地方的典型代表，令你哑口无言，让所有参观者惊叹不已。这是一个棒极了的地方！\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-583\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-2-Copy-1-392x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"392\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n城市中心的建筑是人类历史文化遗产，其风景如画的街道将使步行穿越它们成为一段时间的旅程。在瓦尔帕莱索的历史中心，你将会找到带有海景却又迷宫般错综复杂的房子，其外观拥有生机勃勃的颜色，与太平洋的蔚蓝形成了对比，营造了一个迷人的氛围，每年吸引着成千上万的游客。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-580\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-3-Copy-1-165x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"165\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n作为一个沿海城市，你不得不去游览它的海港，品尝新鲜的海产品和美味的菜肴。商业场所、餐厅和酒吧被波西米亚和休闲氛围占主导地位，还有一些你可以在这个智利的美丽地区所享受的选择，都等待这您的探访。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-581\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-4-Copy-1-332x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"332\" height=\"220\" />[:en]<!--more-->\r\n\r\nLandscapes that will be recorded in your memory.\r\n\r\nAlso known as the jewel of the Pacific, Valparaíso has a varied of cultural activities and beautiful restaurants to offer, here you will always have something to do.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-582\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-1-Copy-1-339x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"339\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nOne option is to visit the Museum of Natural History of Valparaíso, where its extensive variety of flora and fauna, typical of the place, will leave you speechless, to contemplate a playful exhibition that marvels all who visit it. It is an awesome place!\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-583\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-2-Copy-1-392x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"392\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nThe architecture of the city center is a Historical Heritage of Humanity, its picturesque streets will make walking through them a journey in time. In the historic center of Valparaíso you will find a maze of houses with ocean view, whose facades of vibrant colors in contrast to the blue of the Pacific, create a charming atmosphere that attracts hundreds of tourists annually.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-580\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-3-Copy-1-165x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"165\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nBeing a coastal city, you can not stop visiting its port and enjoy the fresh sea products that you can taste in some delicious dish. Commercial premises, restaurants or pubs where the bohemian and casual atmosphere reigns, are some of the alternatives that you can enjoy in this beautiful region of Chile, which awaits your visit.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-581\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-4-Copy-1-332x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"332\" height=\"220\" />[:]', '[:zh]瓦尔帕莱索，太平洋的美人[:en]Valparaíso, beauty of the Pacific.[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e7%93%a6%e5%b0%94%e5%b8%95%e8%8e%b1%e7%b4%a2%ef%bc%8c%e5%a4%aa%e5%b9%b3%e6%b4%8b%e7%9a%84%e7%be%8e%e4%ba%ba', '', '', '2018-11-05 14:47:38', '2018-11-05 14:47:38', '', 0, 'https://anditrip.com/?p=579', 0, 'post', '', 0),
