(603, 1, '2018-11-05 16:10:47', '2018-11-05 16:10:47', '[:zh]巴西与阿根廷所共有的世界奇观\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n伊瓜苏大瀑布的源头为从巴西的巴拉那州流出的伊瓜苏河。当然您也可以在距离阿根廷的米西奥内斯省的伊瓜苏港20公里外的伊瓜苏国家公园中找到一些与之同名的瀑布。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-602\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-1-Copy-3-332x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"332\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n它在1984年被宣布为世界文化遗产，并且在2011年被提名为一个由两个美丽国家所共有的七大自然奇观之一。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-599\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-2-Copy-3-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"293\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n您无法想象这样的一个奇观背后有多么巨大的能量——高达80米的水位差带来的冲击在这茂密的森林中基本是不可比拟的。在这里，您可以在人行道与观景台享受到这种大自然带给您无与伦比的视觉冲击。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-600\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-3-Copy-3-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n不止如此，您还可以做更多。您可以选择参与一个由当地导游所带领的穿越丛林的行程并借此来感受这里的动植物群，您也可以分别到达伊瓜苏瀑布在阿根廷与巴西的两个部分——在这两个国家，您都可以能提供舒适旅行服务的城市来帮助您更好的体验这一奇观。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-601\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-4-Copy-3-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"293\" height=\"220\" />[:en]Brazil and Argentina share a wonder.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nFormed by the Iguazú River that originates in the state of Paraná, Brazil, the falls of the same name are found within the Iguazú National Park, some 20 kilometers from the city of Puerto Iguazú, north of the province of Misiones, Argentina.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-602\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-1-Copy-3-332x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"332\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nDeclared natural heritage of humanity in 1984, in 2011 they were nominated for an international contest as one of the 7 Natural Wonders of the World, shared by two beautiful countries.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-599\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-2-Copy-3-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"293\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nThe energy they transmit is incredible. It treats falls of water of up to 80 meters, in the middle of a dense forest to which it is possible to accede by different means. In the place, there are walkways and viewpoints from which it is possible to contemplate its majesty and enjoy this spectacle of nature.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-600\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-3-Copy-3-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nHowever, you can be more than a spectator. It is possible to take guided tours through the adjacent jungle and admire the great diversity of flora and fauna present in the place. You can get to the Iguazú Falls on the Argentine side or on the Brazilian side, and the cities of both countries have hotels and tourist services so you can get to know this wonder, with all the amenities you want.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-601\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Imagen-4-Copy-3-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"293\" height=\"220\" />[:]', '[:zh]伊瓜苏大瀑布[:en]Iguazu falls[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '598-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-05 16:10:47', '2018-11-05 16:10:47', '', 598, 'https://anditrip.com/598-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
