(622, 1, '2018-11-27 15:02:39', '2018-11-27 15:02:39', '[:zh]如果你想享受一个包括所有最好的南美提供的假期，哥伦比亚是理想的目的地。\r\n快乐、集会和节日。都在这个国家。\r\n\r\n巴兰基利亚狂欢节：巴兰基利亚是一座拥有着温暖气候的工业城市，但它的狂欢节已经赢得了世界的认可。这是哥伦比亚最多资多彩和快乐的庆典。装饰游行、舞蹈以及壮观的服饰只是一部分，如果你在这个季节来巴兰基利亚，你可以尽情享受。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-617\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1colombia_pixabay-Copy-147x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"147\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n麦德林花市：麦德林被誉为春城。由于宜人的气候，美丽的风景和一个蓬勃发展的创新生态系统，使其成为南美最佳旅游地之一。花市是一个你将永远不会后悔参加的活动。这是一个叫silleteros的游行，人们在游行时展出最多样化、五彩斑斓和美丽的花朵，到达只有paisas才能提供的最佳派对节奏。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-618\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/2colombia_pixabay-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n卡利集会：如果有谁被誉为萨尔萨之都，卡利集会将被理解为节日和欢乐的传达。萨尔萨节，选美以及由国内外著名艺术家组成的音乐会使这个集会成为了哥伦比亚最重要的文化活动。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-619\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3colombia_unsplash-Copy-146x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"146\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n在哥伦比亚寻找最美味的咖啡\r\n纳里尼奥：位于哥伦比亚的最西南部，这个省份有着巨大的地理多样性，为培育咖啡提供了众多优势条件，使之成为哥伦比亚咖啡区最重要的产地之一。这里除了是主要的旅游目的地之一，还拥有着美丽的自然风光。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-613\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/4colombia_pixabay-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n安蒂奥基亚：这个省份似乎拥有着一切，咖啡也不例外，因为这里是全国第二大咖啡生产地，由于这里的自然条件、植被和持续的好天气，安蒂奥基亚生产的咖啡尤其的美味，拥有着紧致而又美好的口感，使得咖啡专家与品尝它的人感到愉悦。安蒂奥基亚是哥伦比亚的宝藏。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-614\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/5colombia_pixabay-Copy-332x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"332\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n卡尔达斯、里萨拉尔达、金迪奥和考卡山谷：被联合国教科文组织与2011年命名为世界遗产，这个哥伦比亚的咖啡区拥有着咖啡生产理想的自然与气候条件。话说回来，这是一场感官的盛宴。这里绿色风景被不断的和美味的烤咖啡香气装饰，当地居民为其感到十分自豪。\r\n\r\n最风景如画的村庄\r\n萨伦托、金迪奥：位于亚美尼亚30千米的地方，主街的颜色五彩缤纷，拥有殖民的外观，与当地的本土绿色行程鲜明对比。附近是可可拉山谷，哥伦比亚最具知名度的自然景点之一，你一定不容错过。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-621\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/7colombia_pixabay-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n托利马省的翁达：翁达距离伊瓦格3小时车程，位于马格达莱纳河的边缘，群山环绕的它有很多漂亮的房子，曾是当年西班牙殖民军的总督所生活的地方。你不能错过特兰帕斯街，这里的美味水果会让你流连忘返。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-615\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/8colombia_tolima-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n莱瓦镇：这是一个来源于殖民时期的建筑物群，这里建筑物保存的完好程度让你宛如在进行一次时光旅行。广阔的面积以及周围令人惊叹的自然风光让这个村子成为了哥伦比亚最美的村庄之一，每年也因此能吸引大量的本国人与外国游客。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-616\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/9colombia_pixabay-Copy-400x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:en]Happiness, fairs and festivals. All in one country.\r\n\r\nThe carnival of Barranquilla: Barranquilla is an industrial city with a warm climate, but its carnivals have earned international recognition. It is one of the most colorful and joyful celebrations in Colombia. Parades with tropes, dances and spectacular costumes are just some of the things that you can enjoy when you visit Barranquilla this season.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-617\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1colombia_pixabay-Copy-147x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"147\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nFlowers fair in Medellín: Medellín is known as the city of eternal spring. With a charming climate, beautiful landscapes and an ecosystem of thriving innovation, it has become one of the best destinations in South America. Your flower fair is an event that you will not regret attending. They are parades of \'silleteros\' where they exhibit the most varied, colorful and beautiful flowers, to the rhythm of the best party that only the paisas can offer.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-618\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/2colombia_pixabay-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nCali\'s Fair: If in itself it is known as the capital of salsa, the Cali fairs are translated into festivity and joy in all its expression. Salsa festivals, beauty contests and concerts by famous national and foreign artists make this fair one of the most important cultural events in Colombia.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-619\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3colombia_unsplash-Copy-146x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"146\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nThe best coffee, you find it in Colombia.\r\n\r\nNariño: In the extreme southwest of Colombia, this department with a diverse geography offers multiple advantages for the cultivation of coffee, which has made it one of the main producers of this item in the coffee zone of the country, in addition to one of the main tourist destinations, thanks to its beautiful natural characteristics.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-613\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/4colombia_pixabay-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nAntioquia: This department seems to have everything, and coffee is not the exception, since it is the second producer of this product in the country. Thanks to its natural characteristics, vegetation and constant fresh weather, the coffee obtained in Antioquia is deliciously particular, with an intense and fine flavor that intrigue coffee experts and delight everyone who tastes it. Antioquia is a Colombian treasure that has a lot to offer.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-614\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/5colombia_pixabay-Copy-332x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"332\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nCaldas, Risaralda, Quindío and Valle del Cauca: Inscribed as a world heritage by UNESCO in 2011, this Colombian coffee zone has the ideal natural and climate conditions for coffee production. Take it back, it\'s a party for your senses. The green of its landscapes is adorned with the constant and delicious aroma of roasted coffee, of which its inhabitants feel proud.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-620\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/6colombia_pixabay-Copy-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"293\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nThe most picturesque villages.\r\n\r\nSalento, Quindío: Located about 30km from Armenia, its main street is a celebration of colors and colonial facades that contrast very well with the local green. Nearby is the Cocora Valley, one of the best-known natural attractions of Colombia and that you should also not miss.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-621\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/7colombia_pixabay-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nHonda, Tolima: Seated on the margin of the Magdalena River and bordered by hills and mountains, 3 hours from Ibague is Honda, a town with beautiful houses that were inhabited by the Viceroys of Spain in the colonial era. Calle de Las Trampas and the market square are some of the places you can not miss, to taste the sweet fruits of the region.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-615\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/8colombia_tolima-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nVilla de Leyva, Boyacá: Its beautiful colonial buildings are so well preserved that visiting it is like taking a trip back in time. Its large square and the surrounding nature make Villa de Leyva one of the most picturesque villages in Colombia, with a natural charm that attract locals and foreigners annually.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-616\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/9colombia_pixabay-Copy-400x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:]', '[:zh]哥伦比亚，一个拥有一切的地方。[:en]Colombia, a destination that has everything.[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '612-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-27 15:02:39', '2018-11-27 15:02:39', '', 612, 'https://anditrip.com/612-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(624, 1, '2018-11-27 18:51:00', '2018-11-27 18:51:00', '[:zh]横穿南美大陆的安第斯山脉能给你前所未有的视觉冲击。\r\n\r\n阿根廷的冰川国家公园\r\n这里最著名的景点为佩里托莫雷诺冰川，仅在2016年一年，它就接待了693,584名游客。1981他被联合国教科文组织宣布为世界文化遗产，这也是在整个南美大陆你所能找到的最引人入胜的景观。巨大的冰川组成了让人难忘的画卷——这让游客与当地人都流连忘返。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-629\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1.parque-los-glaciares-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n不仅如此，菲茨罗伊峰拥有3,376米的海拔，这是你所能发现与感受的最美好的景致之一。而且查尔腾镇，一座小巧却美不胜收的小镇，也是巴塔哥尼亚地区所能给予你的最好的礼物之一。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-626\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/2.parque-los-glaciares-Copy-329x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"329\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n.\r\n智利的百内国家公园\r\n蓝宝石般的湖水，拥有多种动植物的森林，都让这个海拔3050米的国家公园在整个南美大陆独一无二。在1979年他被联合国教科文组织宣布为生物圈保护区。多样的生物种类以及自然资源使得它成为了生态旅游与冒险运动的最佳目的地之一，这也是为什么在2013年TripAdvisor称它为世界八大奇迹之一的原因。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-627\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3.parque-torres-del-paine-Copy-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"293\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n在这里，你不仅能在奢华酒店中享受自己，也能在美妙的大自然中找到归属感。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-628\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/4.parque-torres-del-paine2-Copy-294x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"294\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n秘鲁的阿尔帕玛尤山\r\n这座在皑皑白雪覆盖的秘鲁安第斯山脉的山峰在1966举办于德国的一个摄影竞赛中年被选为全世界最美丽山脉之一。行走在拥有5.947米海拔的它之上，你可以感受到安第斯山脉的壮阔之美。这里有足够的泻湖和冰川，连同它所拥有的神秘的气息与风景如画的乡村一起，它成为了一个特殊的目的地，这不仅源于它的自然风光，更是因为它背后的丰富的文化。\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-625\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/5.alpamayo2-Copy-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"293\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:en]The Andes mountain range crosses the continent and gives us incredible landscapes that you can not miss.\r\n\r\nLos Glaciares Park, Argentina.\r\n\r\nIts main attraction is the Perito Moreno Glacier, which in 2016 alone received 693,584 tourists. In 1981 it was declared a World Heritage Site by UNESCO and is one of the most impressive landscapes you can find in the south of the continent. Its majestic masses of ice and the mountains around it, constitute an imposing almost fantastic scenario, which both tourists and locals can not help but admire.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-629\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1.parque-los-glaciares-Copy-330x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nOn the other hand, Mount Fitz Roy with 3,376 m, is one of the most impressive landscapes you can find and walk, and that along with the area of ​​El Chaltén, with all the charm that being a small town at the foot of the mountain confers, it is one of the tourist treasures that Patagonia has for you.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-626\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/2.parque-los-glaciares-Copy-329x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"329\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nTorres del Paine National Park, Chile\r\nLakes of blue waters, beautiful forests with a great diversity of flora and fauna, make this national park one of the richest in the continent. Its main summit reaches 3050 meters above sea level, in 1978 it was declared a Biosphere Reserve by UNESCO, and the diversity of its relief and variety of resources make it one of the best destinations for ecotourism and adventure sports and mountain, reason why in 2013 TripAdvisor Media Group called it the eighth wonder of the world.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-627\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3.parque-torres-del-paine-Copy-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"293\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nThe best thing is that very close you can find beautiful luxury hotels with all the comforts you can access in the city, but with the charm that these wonderful natural spaces have to offer.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-628\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/4.parque-torres-del-paine2-Copy-294x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"294\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\nAlpamayo, Peru.\r\nIn the white mountain range of the Peruvian Andes is this peak that in 1966 was described as \'the most beautiful mountain in the world\', in a scenic photography contest held that year in Germany. Located at 5.947 meters above sea level, it is possible to take a walk around it where you will admire all the flora and fauna of the Andean highlands that are grouped in the place. The lagoons and glaciers are not lacking, and give it that mystical air that, together with its picturesque native villages, make it a special destination not only for its natural characteristics, but also for its cultural richness.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-625\" src=\"https://anditrip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/5.alpamayo2-Copy-293x220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"293\" height=\"220\" />\r\n\r\n<!--more-->[:]', '[:zh]来南美最冷的地方感受一下雪的魅力——[:en]The charm of snow. Know the coldest places in South America.[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e6%9d%a5%e5%8d%97%e7%be%8e%e6%9c%80%e5%86%b7%e7%9a%84%e5%9c%b0%e6%96%b9%e6%84%9f%e5%8f%97%e4%b8%80%e4%b8%8b%e9%9b%aa%e7%9a%84%e9%ad%85%e5%8a%9b', '', '', '2018-11-27 18:51:00', '2018-11-27 18:51:00', '', 0, 'https://anditrip.com/?p=624', 0, 'post', '', 0),
